<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ely" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ely,</orth> 1) seat of a bishop in England: <cit><quote>my lord of E.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 3.4.32" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 4, 32</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>at E. House</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.4.58" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 4, 58</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.216" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 216</bibl>.* 2) the bishop of Ely: <bibl n="shak. r3 4.3.46" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 3, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.3.46" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 3, 46</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.468" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 468</bibl> (Ff in all the three passages: <emph>Morton</emph>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>